data.description: Welcome to 180 Fox Glove Drive, located in the prestigious Lyndhurst Community of Covington. This highly sought-after neighborhood offers an array of amenities, including a clubhouse, fishing opportunities, a fitness center, a homeowners association, a serene lake, nearby schools, a playground, sidewalks, street lights, a swim team, and tennis courts. Get ready to experience the wonderful lifestyle this community has to offer. Step inside this all-brick home with stucco trim and prepare to be amazed. With 6 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this spacious residence provides ample room for your family and guests. The master suite, conveniently located on the main level, offers privacy and tranquility. The common areas of this home are truly grand, providing the perfect backdrop for entertaining and creating lasting memories. The basement is a true standout, featuring a huge wet bar and kitchenette, offering endless possibilities for hosting gatherings or casual nights in. Step outside into your own personal paradise, complete with a stacked stone pool surrounded by majestic live Palm trees. Imagine lounging by the poolside, sipping a refreshing drink, and enjoying the warm Georgia sunshine. This idyllic setting will make you feel like you are on a permanent vacation. This gem of a home won't last long in this desirable community. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property yours. Call now to schedule your appointment and start envisioning the incredible lifestyle that awaits you at 180 Fox Glove Drive in Covington's prestigious Lyndhurst Community.
